00:15:32.870 --> 00:15:33.990
Di mana dia?

00:15:34.120 --> 00:15:35.490
Obito, di belakangmu!

00:15:40.280 --> 00:15:41.080
Mataku!

00:15:43.080 --> 00:15:43.950
Kakashi!

00:15:49.620 --> 00:15:51.240
Shinobi tidak boleh menangis .…

00:15:51.870 --> 00:15:53.280
Aku masih belum mati.

00:15:54.200 --> 00:15:55.160
Jangan sampai lengah.

00:15:56.120 --> 00:15:57.950
<i>Aku hanya bisa bicara .…</i>

00:15:58.990 --> 00:16:01.160
<i>Dan selalu diselamatkan oleh semua orang .…</i>

00:16:02.580 --> 00:16:03.280
<i>Tapi .…</i>

