00:17:04.030 --> 00:17:05.450
Jangan sampai tersandung, Obito.

00:17:05.950 --> 00:17:07.160
Apa kau sudah siap?

00:17:07.530 --> 00:17:08.280
Ya ....

00:17:08.700 --> 00:17:11.030
Aku bersyukur strategi terakhirku bisa kulaksanakan bersamamu.

00:17:12.240 --> 00:17:14.870
Obito ..., Kakashi.

00:17:16.330 --> 00:17:20.030
Obito, kuambil kembali 
semua yang kupinjamkan padamu.

00:17:20.120 --> 00:17:22.990
Terutama mata kiri itu ....

00:17:23.990 --> 00:17:26.280
Apa kau khawatir, Madara?

